+## Overview
+
+Sales ran from 2026-05-02 to 2026-05-21 across four regions and four products. Total revenue was $7,154.44 from 30 orders — a mean of $238.48 per order, with a median order value of $204.94.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget leads with $2,392.00 (33.4% of revenue) from just 16 units, 12.9% ahead of Widget at $2,118.94 (29.6%). Doohickey earned $1,513.00 (21.1%). Sprocket sold the most units by far — 238, or 63.1% of the 377 total — yet returned the least revenue, $1,130.50 (15.8%), because it sells at $4.75 per unit.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North leads with $2,176.35 (30.4%), followed by East at $1,830.79 (25.6%), South at $1,732.48 (24.2%), and West at $1,414.82 (19.8%). Order counts are nearly even (North 8, South 8, East 7, West 7), so the gap comes from order size: the mean order in North is $272.04 versus $202.12 in West, a 34.6% difference.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Grow Gadget sales: 16 units produced $2,392.00 (33.4% of revenue), the highest revenue per unit ($149.50) of any product.
+- Investigate West: its $1,414.82 revenue trails North by 35.0% despite a similar order count (7 vs 8).
+- Review Sprocket pricing: 238 units (63.1% of all units sold) yielded only 15.8% of revenue at $4.75 each.
